cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

This paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques to remove rain from a single image. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel deep learning architecture, which makes it relevant to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of binary maps and recurrent networks suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence techniques, making cs.AI a likely category. The paper also deals with image enhancement, which falls under the category of graphics (cs.GR). Finally, the use of deep learning for image processing suggests the involvement of multimedia (cs.MM) techniques.
